---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const pathname = Astro.url.pathname;
const updated = '2026-05-14';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Arcanesys" lang={lang} description="GDPR-minimal privacy policy. No analytics, no tracking, no third-party sharing. We collect only what is needed to respond to your inquiry.">
  <PageHeader
    lang={lang}
    pathname={pathname}
    titleKey="pageHeader.privacy.title"
    subtitleKey="pageHeader.privacy.subtitle"
  />

  <article class="prose max-w-prose mx-auto px-10 py-12">
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {updated}</p>

    <h2><span class="num">01</span>Who we are</h2>
    <p>
      Arcanesys is the brand operated by Manuel Wegria / Vincent Romagnoli, an independent
      sole-trader entity based in the European Union. Contact:
      <a href="mailto:contact@arcanesys.fr">contact@arcanesys.fr</a>.
    </p>

    <h2><span class="num">02</span>What we collect, when, and why</h2>
    <p>This site collects personal data only when you submit the contact form. Specifically:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, email, organisation, role: to identify and reply to you</li>
      <li>Fleet size and regulatory regime: to assess pilot fit</li>
      <li>Optional free-text problem description: context for the conversation</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Legal basis: <strong>your explicit consent</strong> by submitting the form (GDPR
      Article 6(1)(a)) and our <strong>legitimate interest</strong> in responding (GDPR
      Article 6(1)(f)).
    </p>

    <h2><span class="num">03</span>What we don't do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>No analytics scripts. No Google Analytics, no Facebook Pixel, no tracking pixels.</li>
      <li>No cookies set by us. The site itself uses no cookies.</li>
      <li>No third-party data sharing. We do not sell, rent, or trade your data.</li>
      <li>No newsletter signup, no marketing list, no drip campaigns.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Our form processing is hosted on Netlify (a third party). Netlify acts as a data
      processor. Submitted form fields transit Netlify's infrastructure before reaching us.
      Netlify is a US-based provider. EU-US data transfers are covered by the EU-US Data
      Privacy Framework. If this is a regulatory concern for you, email us directly at
      <a href="mailto:contact@arcanesys.fr">contact@arcanesys.fr</a> instead of using the form.
    </p>

    <h2><span class="num">04</span>How long we keep it</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Active conversation: until the conversation ends.</li>
      <li>After conversation ends: 12 months under legitimate interest (follow-up, audit trail), then deletion.</li>
      <li>If a pilot or commercial relationship begins: data is retained for the duration of that relationship and 5 years after termination, per French commercial accounting obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2><span class="num">05</span>Your rights (GDPR Articles 15–22)</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access the data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Rectify any data that is incorrect</li>
      <li>Have your data erased (right to be forgotten)</li>
      <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
      <li>Data portability: receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      <li>File a complaint with the CNIL (France) or your national data protection authority</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      To exercise any of these rights, email
      <a href="mailto:contact@arcanesys.fr">contact@arcanesys.fr</a> with the subject
      "GDPR request". We respond within 30 days.
    </p>

    <h2><span class="num">06</span>Updates</h2>
    <p>
      We will update this page if our practices change. The "Last updated" date at the top
      reflects the most recent revision. Material changes will be flagged on the home page
      for at least 30 days.
    </p>
  </article>

  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
